Reference

All functions

AOU_species_codes

American Ornithological Union (AOU) species codes for North-American birds

BBS_PA

Pennsylvania Breeding Survey Data (BBS) from the USGS.

BBS_PA_SCTA

Number of Scarlet tanagers (SCTA) observed on Pennsylvania BBS routes in 2006 and total forested landcover in 1km buffers around routes

BBS_PA_combo_cover_1km

Combinations of NLCD land cover classes into more general groups for Pennsylvania, USA.

BBS_PA_landcover_1km

Land cover buffers from the 1 km surrounding Breeding Bird Survey Routes (BBS) in Pennsylvania

NA_to_zero()

Change all NA values (missing vlaues) in a column to zero

aa_chars

Characteristics of amino acids

aa_chars_subset

Characteristics of amino acids (subset)

antlers

Simulated data on the effects of diet on deer antlers

blastr()

Execute BLAST from R.

brook_trout

Brook trout impacts on Chinook salmon survival - original data

brook_trout_ABD

Impact of brook trout on survival of Chinook salmon in Idaho.

chargaff1951

Data from publications by Chargaff 1951

combine_NLCD_classes()

Combine multiple landcover classes into a single combined group

dengueseq_fasta

dengueseq_fasta

diag_show()

Print the diagonal of a matrix

doves_PA

PA Mourning doves

doves_PA_3_years

PA Mourning doves from 3 years, 2005, 2007 and 2010

eaglesOH

Eagles in Ohio dataset

eaglesPA

Eagles in Pennsylvania dataset

eaglesWV

Eagles in West Virginia (WV) dataset#' A dataset containing the number of nesting pairs of eagles found in West Virginia, USA, from 1980 through 2007 Data is not available for all years and is given as NA. Important dates: 1963 417 pairs in all of continental USA 1966 endangered spp act 1967 listed 1972 DDT banned

eggs

Bird eggs datatset.

eggs_and_nests

Egg data combined with data on nests

eggs_and_nests2

Subset of eggs_and_nests data the contains only Dome, Cup, and ground surface nests

expand_BBS_routes()

Expand BBS data to include zeros when a species was not seen.

fasta_cleaner()

Function to convert a FASTA file stored as an object into a vector

findPotentialStartsAndStops()

Function to identify potential start and stop codons

frogarms

Data on the body size and arm girth of male and female Australian Quacking Frogs (Crinia georgiana)

generateSeqsWithMultinomialModel()

generateSeqsWithMultinomialModel

hShroom2

hShroom2

hShroom3

hShroom3

human_bodytemp

Human body temperature data and heartrate

human_gene_lengths

Lengths of human genes

mShroom3a

mShroom3a

make_dateset_helpfile()

Create template for dataset documentation

make_my_data2L()

Extract random subset of a dataframe

milk

Mammal milk dataset

pams

Point-accepted mutation (PAM) data matrix from Dayoff et al. 1978

pikas

Data on presence of pikas and marmots from Front Range Pika Project

printPairwiseAlignment()

printPairwiseAlignment

sShroom

sShroom

sample_BBS_routes()

Select random subset of Breeding Bird Survey (BBS) routes

sample_dove_routes()

Select random subset of Breeding Bird Survey (BBS) routes

shroom_table

Print the lower or upper triangular part of a matrix flextable

Data on the size of Trillium from several sites in Crawford County, PA

Show the tutorials currently available for the dayoff package

Function to update dayoff package

Data on species richness in constructed wetlands at Pennsylvania Game Lands 297 in south western PA.

wine

Wine recognition data

woodcock_MI_3_years

Subset of Woodcock call survey data from Michigan, USA
